# Bottlenose Dolphin Whistle Classifier
### Raven Pro Selection Tables + SEANOE Public Dataset

#**Pipeline:**
#1. Load Raven `.txt` selection tables → parse whistle timestamps from your recordings
#2. Load SEANOE public dataset → pre-cut whistle clips (positives) + noise segments (negatives)
#3. Combine both sources into one training set
#4. Oversample whistle frames to fix class imbalance
#5. Train binary CNN (whistle vs noise)
#6. Run inference on your recordings → frame-level probability CSV
#7. Detect whistle events via state flips → chop WAV into clips

